data.description: Located in one of Denver's most desirable neighborhoods, Winston Downs, this light-filled, meticulously maintained, mid-century brick ranch home is not to be missed. Featuring an open floor plan, large picture windows showcasing mountain views, original gleaming hardwood floors, central air & whole house fan, as well as 2 fireplaces. The eat-in kitchen w/ walk-in pantry that opens to a large great room, full wet bar, formal living & dining, covered patio & mature landscaping w/ large shade trees make this home an entertainer's dream. Ample storage as well as an over sized 2 car garage w/ overhead storage, & new air conditioning & furnace ('05), hot water heater ('09), & electrical service ('08) complete this wonderful home. Winston Downs is an established community where families often choose to make their home for many years. Enjoy this quiet, tucked-away neighborhood w/out sacrificing the convenience of being close to the city...Downtown & the DTC are a quick commute away!
